flowchart TD
    A[Project or Feature Request] --> B[Create or update SPEC.md]
    B --> E[Create or update ARCHITECTURE.md and SETUP.md]
    B --> F[Create or update ROADMAP.md and RISKS.md]
    E --> G[Create FEATURE_ANALYSIS.md]
    F --> G
    G --> H{Architecture decision needed?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Create ADR_*.md or update DECISIONS.md]
    H -->|No| J[Create FEATURE_PLAN.md]
    I --> J
    J --> K[Create or update TEST_PLAN.md or QA.md]
    K --> L[Implement in phases]
    L --> M{Issue found?}
    M -->|Yes| N[Create FEATURE_ISSUE.md]
    N --> G
    M -->|No| O{Large change or drift?}
    O -->|Yes| P[Create FEATURE_REFACTOR.md]
    O -->|No| Q[Update FEATURE_DOC.md and API_REFERENCE.md]
    P --> L
    Q --> R[Update README.md and CHANGELOG.md]
    R --> S[Prepare PUBLISH.md]
    S --> T[Retrospective for milestone or release]
    T --> U[Release or publish]
    T -.->|Feed back lessons| E
    T -.->|Feed back lessons| F
